Package jakarta.security.enterprise.authentication.mechanism.http

Annotation Type FormAuthenticationMechanismDefinition

@Retention(RUNTIME)
@Target(TYPE)
public @interface FormAuthenticationMechanismDefinition
Annotation used to define a container authentication mechanism that implements FORM authentication as defined by the Servlet spec (13.6.3) and make that implementation available as an enabled CDI bean.
